steps.name: Login With valid credentials
Click Management and click Contract Pricing
"Find Pricing" window is open and click Add button
"Add Contract Pricing" window is open
Click elipsis bytton next to the Custoner field
"Find Facility" window is open
Enter "My First Customer" into search criteria and click Find button
Click OK button
Click ellipsis button next to the Working Facility field
"Find Facility" window is open
Enter "My Lab" into Facility Name search criteria and click Find button
Click OK button
Click ellipsis button next to Type Procedure Default field
"Find Type Procedure Default" window is open
Find "Description" by entering Types Description and click Find button
Click OK button
Enter Contract Pricing "03/25/2022"
Click Save button and save Contract Pricing
Enter Pricing "04/25/2022"
Click Save button and save Contract Pricing
Enter "257.50" to the Price field
Click Save button and click Close button to close Contract Pricing screen
